flew 100 feet through the air, and landed on my unprotected head.  I was in the hospital 16 months - the first three in a coma.  That is when I had brain surgery.  When out of the hospital, returning to drywall construction was not an option, so I enrolled in College of the Desert and studied computer science and information systems.  Worked full-time in the field seven years while attending college part-time.  Graduated with certificate in 1999, but had a second motorcycle accident five months later.  Broke my neck that time, and old injuries relapsed from my 1991 motorcycle accident.  I've been on disability since, but volunteered five years in a computer clinic while living in OC and five years at Aquarium of the Pacific while living in Long Beach.  But then I decided to return to college and earn a degree.  In 2017 I broke my hip in a bicycle accident, and while recovering from total hip replacement, changed my major to web development...  </p>","            <p>Hobbies:</p>","               <ul>","                   <li>Biking</li>","                   <li>Weight lifting</li>","                   <li>Swimming</li>","                   <li>Beach walks</li>","                   <li>Building/maintaining bikes</li>","                   <li>Building/programming/using computers</li>","               </ul>","            <a href=\"https://github.com/github-patrixweb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Patrick Olesiak's Profile on GitHub\">Patrick Olesiak's Profile on GitHub</a>","   <?php","        /*","        ","        lab1.php","        Patrick Olesiak","        August 31, 2019","        ","        ","        @@@@@@@@@@@@@@","        */","        #output a paragragh in HTML","        echo \"<p>After my 1999 motorcycle accident, I did not ride for 16++ years.  However, in 2016 I decided to try an adult tricycle; that worked out for me due to recent balance issues.  Since that time, I assembled two of them.  And I often query Google about bike repair and maintenance questions.  One site that repeatedly came up with user threads on the subject is <a href='https://bikeforums.net' target='_blank'>Bike Forums</a>.  And for parts and accessories,I find <a href='https://www.amazon.com/s?k=cycling+accessories+for+bike&gclid=Cj0KCQjw2K3rBRDiARIsAOFSW_47iUiy1a4TvNUBSdYVsd_0-T19dpwpwuBK5Kl6iIJAPnTUmBPPZiUaAs-4EALw_wcB&hvadid=323347530889&hvdev=c&hvlocphy=9031542&hvnetw=g&hvpos=1t1&hvqmt=b&hvrand=5029445381829406785&hvtargid=kwd-505162740637&hydadcr=8590_9892164&tag=googhydr-20&ref=pd_sl_1270l2qu3v_b' target='_blank'>Amazon </a> is budget friendly.</p>","        <p>This assignment was frustrating because it seemed like the cloud technologies involved were working against me.  But I learned about computers before the cloud was mainstream, so I will chalk this up as new experience and it'll get better for me with time.   ","        </p>\";","        ","    ?>",""],"id":7}],[{"start":{"row":1,"column":18},"end":{"row":1,"column":41},"action":"remove","lines":["http://www.example.com/"],"id":8},{"start":{"row":1,"column":18},"end":{"row":1,"column":71},"action":"insert","lines":["https://patrixweb.herokuapp.com/labwork/lab1/lab1.php"]}],[{"start":{"row":3,"column":69},"end":{"row":4,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""],"id":9},{"start":{"row":4,"column":0},"end":{"row":5,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""]}],[{"start":{"row":4,"column":0},"end":{"row":5,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""],"id":10}],[{"start":{"row":5,"column":0},"end":{"row":5,"column":1},"action":"insert","lines":["I"],"id":11},{"start":{"row":5,"column":1},"end":{"row":5,"column":2},"action":"insert","lines":["n"]},{"start":{"row":5,"column":2},"end":{"row":5,"column":3},"action":"insert","lines":["s"]}],[{"start":{"row":5,"column":3},"end":{"row":5,"column":4},"action":"insert","lines":["t"],"id":12},{"start":{"row":5,"column":4},"end":{"row":5,"column":5},"action":"insert","lines":["a"]},{"start":{"row":5,"column":5},"end":{"row":5,"column":6},"action"